Name: Buy Low Sell High
About the game: Buy Low Sell High is a stock market game with a simple goal: make as much money as possible. With over 40 unique companies and 8 industries to choose from, there are plenty of ways to make your money. However markets can be unpredictable.. use news stories to pick up on market trends to get ahead of the curve on upcoming price changes. Good luck and get rich! Earnings View your earnings changing in real time to get immediate feedback on which investments are making you money, and which ones are costing you. Purchase History Every decision you make is logged so you can go back and review how your stocks have done over the course of the game. News Stories Each stock has unique news stories that spark price changes and will affect long term trends for each company. Milestones Milestones help track progression, give objectives to work towards, and provides rewards for completing goals.
